A World Without Email: Reimagining Work in an Age of Communication Overload

By Cal Newport

People are not designed to be in constant digital communication.
Is mail, the leading technology of its time, now becoming a mechanism that reduces efficiency?

This book shows us that it’s time for clear and strong changes and walks us through how to do it.
